The following demos illustrate how [incr Tcl] can be used to support
object-oriented programming in Tcl.

    coloredit ......... demonstrates ColorEditor/FilteredBox
    listboxes ......... demonstrates ListBox/SelectBox/FilteredBox

In addition, the following directories contain example code:

    toasters .......... classes for the "toaster" example described
                        in the paper "Intro.ps"

    counters .......... example of "counter" class that has been a
                        focus of discussion on the internet

    widgets ........... example code for "mega-widgets"
